710,IssueCommentEvent,2016-10-27 21:27:24+00:00,57714220,rabitt/pysox,3009670,justinsalamon,,,185749981,256774942,"> I see your point, but my personal preference is to avoid having input_file = output_file, because it's harder to find and reproduce bugs. Why not just do:
```
