1827,IssueCommentEvent,2015-07-15 14:08:59+00:00,26481039,zerwes/hiyapyco,9654986,zerwes,,,95058668,121626630,"You are right the '{{' delimiters are the problem.
PyYAML will only accept them insight of quotes.
And the YAML cast `a: !!int {{ a + b }}` will not work as the string must first be interpolated!
I have implemented a `castinterpolated` (defaults to *False*) arg that will try to cast the interpolated string if possible (*float*, *int* or *bool*) in **0.4.1**
Give it a try.
Hope this helps.",{},,User,False
