2606,IssueCommentEvent,2017-10-06 09:47:55+00:00,47879364,pklaus/brother_ql,86426,splitbrain,,,263384585,334709947,"Okay, so the timeout seems to define how long a whole send operation is allowed to take. The default of 0.01 is much too small. Using the following now prints successfully:

