4952,IssueCommentEvent,2016-04-28 02:59:45+00:00,4386648,earwig/mwparserfromhell,4588496,ricordisamoa,,,151520846,215296553,"Changing an external link into a template requires changing the type.

This seems to work:
```python
for link in code.filter_external_links():
    # link is '[http://example.com/ Example]'
    newstr = '{{tpl|url=' + str(link.url) + '|name=' + str(link.title) + '}}'
    code.nodes[code.index(link)] = mwparserfromhell.parse(newstr)
```

or with Template constructor:
```python
for link in code.filter_external_links():
    # link is '[http://example.com/ Example]'
    tpl = mwparserfromhell.nodes.template.Template('tpl')
    tpl.add('url', link.url)
    tpl.add('name', link.title)
    code.nodes[code.index(link)] = tpl
```",{},,User,False
