5788,IssueCommentEvent,2016-09-28 13:37:05+00:00,42185087,James1345/django-rest-knox,777095,tr00st,,,138340080,250168458,"@pylixm, looks like the problem is that you've disabled the BasicAuthentication class, and are then attempting to use basic authentication - you'll need to uncomment the BasicAuthentication line in the DEFAULT_AUTHENTICATION_CLASSES entry.

