6422,IssueCommentEvent,2016-09-01 09:35:19+00:00,6241977,deschler/django-modeltranslation,1769916,zlorf,,,129455430,244027700,"This `en_us` is not weird at all - object titles are computed at the time of django app bootstrap, and its performed under `en_us` language. User language (like `fr`) is activated only during requests (when request from browser carry language info), but titles for choice fields were already computed.

Closing for now, as it not solveable using MT due to architecture approach.",{},,User,False
