6538,IssueCommentEvent,2015-08-06 10:21:05+00:00,7607807,mjumbewu/django-rest-framework-csv,6632349,elnygren,,,99381160,128317442,"okey I have this kind of solution for myself:

```python
class MyViewSet(..):
  renderer_classes = renderer_classes = api_settings.DEFAULT_RENDERER_CLASSES + [r.CSVRenderer, ]

  def __init__(self, *args, **kwargs):
    r.CSVRenderer.writer_opts = {
      'quoting': csv.QUOTE_ALL,
      'quotechar': '""',
      'delimiter': ';'
      }
    super(MyViewSet, self).__init__(*args, **kwargs)
```
Implementation (all tox tests pass):
https://github.com/elnygren/django-rest-framework-csv/commit/eebe6d5b5236524a65f6b0761a000647425b211d

I suppose a better way would be to use the Django settings though? (which is why I haven't created a PR)",{},,User,False
