8522,IssueCommentEvent,2016-01-01 01:33:20+00:00,24757484,robotpy/robotpy-wpilib,1538432,james-ward,640276,robotpy,53843510,168273250,"The hanging on the built in tests is due to an issue with threading in the test harness.

