We already have [fa-lg](https://github.com/FortAwesome/Font-Awesome/blob/master/css/font-awesome.css#L23) which sets font size at 1.3em

If you need 1.5, please use custom css. It is as easy as:
```css
.fa-1_5x {
  font-size: 1.5em;
} 
```

Closing here",{},MEMBER,User,False
