10249,IssueCommentEvent,2015-07-02 08:18:36+00:00,3470471,FortAwesome/Font-Awesome,956290,lukeoliff,1505683,FortAwesome,28891991,117954373,"I was able to do this with the following;

````
.fa-aud::before {
    font-family: ""Montserrat"",​Arial,​sans-serif;
    content: ""A"";
}

.fa-aud::after {
    content: """";
}

.fa-nzd::before {
    font-family: ""Montserrat"",​Arial,​sans-serif;
    content: ""NZ"";
}

.fa-nzd::after {
    content: """";
}
````",{},,User,False
