11480,IssueCommentEvent,2016-02-29 21:42:58+00:00,7209075,pantsbuild/pants,7378,baroquebobcat,3065172,pantsbuild,54660180,190408818,"From my doc digging, it looks like you need to also update your resolver chain in order to allow for mutable's changes to `ivy.xml` to work.

This is because ivy tries to be lazy and won't bother checking past the cache unless the whole resolver chain says it's ok to look for modified artifacts.

There's some discussion of this behavior on http://stackoverflow.com/questions/2748646/ivy-resolve-not-working-with-dynamic-artifact",{},,User,False
