12108,IssueCommentEvent,2017-06-08 12:50:41+00:00,50359589,girder/girder_worker,669959,kotfic,5150517,girder,232347529,307093415,"I have recently pushed docker container images to dockerhub.  The new way to test this is as follows:

Create a virtual environment and cd into a working directory 
```sh
# Install girder-worker
git clone https://github.com/girder/girder_worker.git .
git checkout integration-test-framework
pip install -e .

# Run the integration environment
cd tests/integration
docker-compose up

# From a separate terminal - Run the test suite
cd tests/integration
pip install -r requirements.txt
pytest -v  
```

",{},,User,False
