12362,IssueCommentEvent,2018-01-17 22:41:20+00:00,32382669,crossbario/txaio,145599,meejah,5656948,crossbario,289437040,358474038,"txaio is for programming a library that uses asyncio *or* twisted. It doesn't have provisions for using both at once in the same process.

The most-likely way forward would be to do one of two things

 - create a Twisted reactor implementation that ""runs on top"" of the asyncio reactor
 - create an asyncio event-loop implementation that ""runs on top"" of Twisted

If one of those two things existed, then it might be feasible to make txaio support both twisted and asyncio within the same process -- but you'd still need to take care to have the correct Deferreds/Futures be dealt with on the correct event-loop.
",{},MEMBER,User,False
