I've never seen that before, so I'll have to do some testing to see how our parser is handling parentheses. I think it just ignores them, but I'm not sure. I created [a new issue][2] for following up on that.

In the meantime, this looks great. Pulling now, and it will be deployed soon.

[1]: https://www.courtlistener.com/?q=%22Pac.2d%22
[2]: https://github.com/freelawproject/courtlistener/issues/571",{},,User,False
