12654,IssueCommentEvent,2015-02-20 18:30:09+00:00,11589713,deis/deis,968339,phspagiari,6117407,deis,58364518,75293324,"So @mboersma I didnt set this variable, the deis is looking for the units at $HOME/.deis/units indeed. But I look more deep into the problem of etcd/fleet and after some tests I found that some of etcd servers of the cluster is not working.

