12717,IssueCommentEvent,2018-08-23 10:40:47+00:00,71996613,blue-yonder/tsfresh,96679,earthgecko,6234170,blue-yonder,352956790,415371409,"Hi @joel-wilson yes playing with an example of your data set converted to a dataframe of:

