12788,IssueCommentEvent,2018-03-07 23:17:38+00:00,56251096,ethereum/web3.py,8933231,dylanjw,6250754,ethereum,297701123,371320497,"To complete this PR another issue involving the eth-tester gas estimation must be resolved.  This is the issue im having.

