12906,IssueCommentEvent,2015-10-07 09:41:29+00:00,6235174,conda/conda,293525,ijstokes,6392739,conda,34467202,146133788,"@csoja and @ilanschnell I've had some discussions with @stephenakearns and @mrduane about the importance of strong Windows support in Anaconda.  I think we're on the same page with @teoliphant @pzwang, MattH and MicheleC.  Anaconda (and by implication conda) working wonderfully perfectly in Windows, using Powershell, cygwin, and msysgit (or similar) would really be appreciated.",{},,User,False
