My log showed that I routinely ran pip and conda with sudo :-(

I fixed the problem by deleting the entire ~/anaconda directory
and reinstalling from scratch.

Best regards,
Tom

On Thu, Jan 21, 2016 at 06:09:17AM -0800, Mike Sarahan wrote:
> One thing that might cause this sort of error is if files are in use by
> some running Python process.  Please make sure to kill all running IPython
