13036,IssueCommentEvent,2015-04-16 08:52:12+00:00,16557526,pysam-developers/pysam,4426336,AndreasHeger,6598771,pysam-developers,68420575,93681644,"                                                                                      Thanks, I will take a look. Best, andreas                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Sent from my BlackBerry 10 smartphone on the EE network.                                                                                                                                                                                                                From: Danny ColliganSent: Wednesday, 15 April 2015 23:56To: pysam-developers/pysamReply To: pysam-developers/pysamCc: Andreas HegerSubject: Re: [pysam] Pysam hangs on remote BAM fetch when server doesn't implement byte serving (#107)I'm not sure what code paths in samtools would trigger it, but AFAICT it looks like a pysam-only problem.  Here is a session using the same file served by the same non-byte-serving server:

