13084,IssueCommentEvent,2017-04-25 01:44:38+00:00,12235583,elastic/curator,1020383,untergeek,6764390,elastic,223993912,296868009,"Unfortunately, no.

[Read about the native python client call](http://elasticsearch-py.readthedocs.io/en/master/api.html#elasticsearch.client.SnapshotClient.delete) (note, no options for anything other than _master node_ timeout.)

[Read the official API documentation](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/5.3/modules-snapshots.html) (again, no options for timeout of any kind).

