13204,IssueCommentEvent,2017-10-13 17:23:41+00:00,51040886,Azure/azure-cli,1050156,lmazuel,6844498,Azure,264809927,336515469,"@WilliamBerryiii the problem here is that the service returns a **string** `ServiceConnect, DeviceConnect, RegistryWrite` and not an array... And this one is not defined as a valid string in the RestAPI specification I use to generate the SDK:
