14214,IssueCommentEvent,2016-02-27 20:12:09+00:00,39923176,BD2KGenomics/toil-scripts,5143256,hannes-ucsc,8701293,BD2KGenomics,136173635,189715711,"One thing to keep in mind is that SSH agent forwarding doesn't work well with screen.

https://gist.github.com/martijnvermaat/8070533

So running `ssh` or `cgcloud ssh` in a reattached screen on the head node will fail if you are relying on agent forwarding for authentication. To fix, we should use a dedicated key pair on the head node. I've modified the above instructions (look for *new*).

In any case, don't put your own private keys on the head node.",{},,User,False
