14710,IssueCommentEvent,2015-12-15 20:53:30+00:00,4235447,django-salesforce/django-salesforce,1261962,chromakey,9872531,django-salesforce,122353810,164893528,"```
python manage.py inspectdb --help
```
returns this optional argument
```
  --database DATABASE   Nominates a database to introspect. Defaults to using
                        the ""default"" database.
```

Try it without the ""="".  i.e.

```
python manage.py inspectdb --database salesforce
```

This is a change from <= Django 1.8",{},,User,False
