14982,IssueCommentEvent,2015-06-10 22:53:58+00:00,14284859,marshmallow-code/marshmallow,7722913,philtay,10334301,marshmallow-code,80948096,110940571,"Ok, but I don't want to push even more logic in an already semi-spaghettish function. It looks like `_run_validator` is meant for schema-level validation only. I can rename it to `_validate_schema` and add another function `_validate_field`. I will use the latter to implement `@validates`. Ok?",{},,User,False
