15429,IssueCommentEvent,2016-03-24 21:03:17+00:00,32944298,Z3Prover/z3,511795,delcypher,11668813,Z3Prover,143114923,201019935,"Okay just to note there are also a few other ways to set the include directories apart from appending to ``Z3_COMPONENT_EXTRA_INCLUDE_DIRS``.

You can do it on a per-target basis (the recommended way)

```cmake
target_include_directories(util PRIVATE ""${CMAKE_SOURCE_DIR}/src"")
```

or globally (not recommended)

```cmake
include_directories(""${CMAKE_SOURCE_DIR}/src"")
```
