17029,IssueCommentEvent,2017-03-16 16:06:40+00:00,38581626,pybind/pybind11,4831417,dean0x7d,17565521,pybind,214743879,287106371,"Try changing
```c++
py::class_<PyPropertyGridListPage>(m, ""PropertyGridListPage"", ListBox, PropertyGridPage)
```
to
```c++
py::class_<PyPropertyGridListPage, PyListBox, PyPropertyGridPage>(m, ""PropertyGridListPage"")
```
