17397,IssueCommentEvent,2016-07-31 10:06:26+00:00,13775110,scour-project/scour,233340,oberstet,19892970,scour-project,163820531,236421659,"@Perhelion Ok, seems I was wrong on that. So for SVG using a doctype is actively discouraged, and even for XML in general, it is [optional](https://www.w3.org/TR/2004/REC-xml11-20040204/#NT-prolog). Consequently, there should be a `--remove-doctype` option with default `true`. @Ede123 opinions?",{},,User,False
