17822,IssueCommentEvent,2017-03-27 13:31:10+00:00,68402336,streamlink/streamlink,8580211,enzanki-ars,22243823,streamlink,216274153,289453794,"@gravyboat No problem.  I understand the intent of both of your messages.  Sorry about not being clear with the intent of my reply.  I was just responding to confirm my understanding of your point. I should have also stated that there was no reason to my sorting method.  I just used what was pre-existing.  

Currently, I see 3 main choices in sorting:

1. `['alt_streams_(worst->best)', 'primary_streams_(worst->best)', 'worst', 'best']`
2. `['worst', 'alt_streams_(worst->best)', 'primary_streams_(worst->best)', 'best']`
3. `['best', 'primary_streams_(best->worst)', 'alt_streams_(best->worst)', 'worst']`

My personal preference may lean a little more towards option 2 or 3, but there may be others that I did not think of.",{},,User,False
