17835,IssueCommentEvent,2017-02-25 14:59:59+00:00,68402336,streamlink/streamlink,19405280,starchivore,22243823,streamlink,209469067,282489188,"I've been getting the `URL` of `M3U8` manually since they switched to the new CDN in January and they're definitely blocking my location, though the old CDN is still accessible without proxy.

Maybe it takes time to write something for `--animelab-username` and `--animelab-password` since they're restricting everything for logged on (free and paid) users in AU/NZ only, at least it's SUPER easy to grab the direct links to `mp4` files afterwards but they're still serving hard-subbed episodes:

https://www.animelab.com/player/dragon-ball-super-episode-79

That's really up to you since it's yet another backup for me just in case other streaming providers are getting smarter or something, and it's also slow beyond imagination to get something via free proxy servers. Maybe some Aussies do appreciate a plugin and that could be done without having to spend much time.",{},,User,False
