17842,IssueCommentEvent,2017-01-03 16:29:29+00:00,68402336,streamlink/streamlink,1496148,javiercantero,22243823,streamlink,198458562,270155999,"@beardypig The calls to `/api/channels/<channel>/subscription` and `/api/channels/<channel>/viewer` aren't part of the public API[1], so not a good idea to try to provide them to third party apps in the first place.

