18038,IssueCommentEvent,2018-04-25 19:48:06+00:00,42155092,python-rapidjson/python-rapidjson,412797,lelit,25253642,python-rapidjson,310337113,384411734,"Uhm, I stand corrected, there was a glitch in the pytest parametrization...

```
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- benchmark 'Ensure ASCII string: deserialize': 2 tests ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Name (time in us)                                          Min                 Max                Mean            StdDev              Median               IQR            Outliers  OPS (Kops/s)            Rounds  Iterations
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
test_loads_plain_ascii[UTF8-Ensure ASCII string]       55.2730 (1.0)      111.8980 (1.0)       55.9388 (1.0)      1.8668 (1.0)       55.7290 (1.0)      0.4070 (1.0)       268;500       17.8767 (1.0)       13178           1
test_loads_plain_ascii[ASCII-Ensure ASCII string]     101.7080 (1.84)     181.9020 (1.63)     103.4041 (1.85)     3.5641 (1.91)     102.6190 (1.84)     0.5450 (1.34)     421;1277        9.6708 (0.54)       9435           1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ benchmark 'Ensure ASCII string: serialize': 2 tests -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Name (time in us)                                          Min                 Max                Mean            StdDev              Median               IQR            Outliers  OPS (Kops/s)            Rounds  Iterations
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
test_dumps_plain_ascii[UTF8-Ensure ASCII string]       58.6200 (1.0)      106.2680 (1.0)       60.1724 (1.0)      2.2044 (1.0)       59.7330 (1.0)      0.4600 (1.0)       526;740       16.6189 (1.0)       10821           1
test_dumps_plain_ascii[ASCII-Ensure ASCII string]     105.9980 (1.81)     201.5630 (1.90)     108.9658 (1.81)     3.7346 (1.69)     108.2050 (1.81)     1.3070 (2.84)      349;891        9.1772 (0.55)       8846           1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
```

And this more reasonable, given that:
```
>>> import rapidjson
>>> a=""привет, мир!""*1000
>>> print(len(rapidjson.dumps(a, ensure_ascii=False)))
12002
>>> print(len(rapidjson.dumps(a, ensure_ascii=True)))
57002
```
